# Turnip v2.2.0 A8XX Custom Driver Implementation

## Objective
Review existing Turnip driver profiles (v1.8.8, v1.9.2, v2.0.0), research and correctly configure Adreno 8xx series profiles (810, 825, 829, 830, 840), and build the new `v2.2.0` in two variants: `-p` (Performance, with forced max GPU clocks) and `-b` (Balanced). 

